-in-Guatemala-750x443.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-750x443.png 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-1090x644.png 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-210x124.png 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-768x454.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-1536x907.png 1536w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala.png 1740w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="72491" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2023/10/25/food-shortage-in-a-height-chart/hunger-crisis-in-guatemala/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala.png" data-orig-size="1740,1028" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="hunger crisis in Guatemala" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-750x443.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunger-crisis-in-Guatemala-1090x644.png" /></a></p><p>危地马拉面临粮食短缺。路透社的 Cassandra Garrison、Clare Trainor 和 Sarah Slobin 使用<a href="https://www.reuters.com/graphics/GUATEMALA-CLIMATECHANGE/HUNGER/jnvwwbjzyvw/">身高图表来显示生长发育迟缓的指标</a>。</p><blockquote><p>八月的一天，玛丽亚·康塞普西翁·罗德里格斯 (Maria Concepcion Rodr